name: DOMINANT & WITCH
description: She came at his call.   She always comes when he needs her.   His soul is in her, she is the secret keeper of his soul.   Passion, emotions, hellish disposition - everything is perfectly combined in her.  Master and submissive.   Lord and servant.   Dominant and witch.    Their union is unbreakable.   They will continue to turn into other people's lives, so that the life of the lovers does not turn into a bunch of dirty gray everyday life.
